metadata.title: MUSHY
metadata.visionDescription: A cartoon-style illustration of a yellow bird with a round face and wide, expressive eyes. The bird has an orange beak and is wearing a blue and beige winter hat with a pom-pom. The background is solid black, which contrasts with the bright colors of the character, making it stand out. The drawing has bold outlines and a simplistic, playful style.

metadata.title: hornet
metadata.visionDescription: The image depicts a stylized, pixel art character standing in a green environment. The character wears a red cape and has a distinctive white, horned mask with black eye holes. It holds a long, sword-like weapon in its slender, black arms. The background consists of various shades of green, suggesting foliage and a forest-like setting. The art style is minimalistic with blocky, pixelated shapes and flat colors, emphasizing a retro, video game aesthetic.

metadata.title: sharky1
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a cute, animated yellow shark with a big smile and large, wide eyes. The shark has a white underbelly and is depicted in a playful pose, surrounded by blue bubbles and a splash of water. The style is cartoonish and vibrant, with bold outlines and simple shapes, giving it a cheerful and friendly appearance.

metadata.title: stingray
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a simplified, stylized drawing of a person with brown hair wearing a blue shirt from a rear view. The background is a large, irregularly shaped blue oval. Surrounding the person are three abstract, dark blue shapes resembling stylized animal ears or horns. The style is cartoonish with basic lines and flat colors, giving it a minimalist, modern feel.
